String.Dest: Last guy didn't sit for a week. Didn't even know what hit him.

String.Source: What? No, I didn't do anything. I mean... Just forget it.
String.Dest: What? No, I didn't do anything. I mean... Just forget it.

String.Source: You bet. I'm dying for some target practice.
String.Dest: You bet. I'm dying for some target practice.

String.Source: Hell yeah, we find that Operator recon team and put them in the ground.

String.Source: But, uh, now that you mention it...
String.Dest: But, uh, now that you mention it...

String.Source: Jesus. It won't happen again. It's just... after Maven died...
String.Dest: Jesus. It won't happen again. It's just... after Maven died...

String.Source: Oh was that a threat? I'm scared. I really am.
String.Dest: Oh was that a threat? I'm scared. I really am.

String.Source: Well, with a face like that, you really should reconsider.
String.Dest: Well, with a face like that, you really should reconsider.

String.Source: No, goddamn it. Keep your voice down. I was talking about spooking the traders.
String.Dest: No, goddamn it. Keep your voice down. I was talking about spooking the traders.

String.Source: I'm still finding random remains in my gear from that night.
String.Dest: I'm still finding random remains in my gear from that night.

String.Source: You thinking what I'm thinking?
String.Dest: You thinking what I'm thinking?

String.Source: You look like you robbed a child to put that outfit together.
String.Dest: You look like you robbed a child to put that outfit together.

String.Source: Hey, Savoy, up for a night run? We're putting one together for tomorrow.
String.Dest: Hey, Savoy, up for a night run? We're putting one together for tomorrow.

String.Source: Why? You screw something up?
String.Dest: Why? You screw something up?

String.Source: Oh, jesus, what's that smell?
String.Dest: Oh, jesus, what's that smell?

String.Source: Oh look who's back. I thought the wasteland would have taken care of you.
String.Dest: Oh look who's back. I thought the wasteland would have taken care of you.

String.Source: I'm not sure what's worse: sharing this park with Pack animals or Operator brats.
String.Dest: I'm not sure what's worse: sharing this park with Pack animals or Operator brats.

String.Source: Least we don't hide behind masks.
String.Dest: Least we don't hide behind masks.

String.Source: They'll never track it back to me. As far as they know, they were lost in the wasteland.
String.Dest: They'll never track it back to me. As far as they know, they were lost in the wasteland.

String.Source: Did you figure it out yet?
String.Dest: Did you figure it out yet?

String.Source: I'm putting you on guard duty, starting tomorrow.
String.Dest: I'm putting you on guard duty, starting tomorrow.

String.Source: Pass. I love Dixie, but the last time I went out with her, I had enough "fun" to last two lifetimes.
String.Dest: Pass. I love Dixie, but the last time I went out with her, I had enough "fun" to last two lifetimes.

String.Source: Hey, you up for a night run tomorrow?
String.Dest: Hey, you up for a night run tomorrow?

String.Source: Are you kidding me? I'm one of the best you've got.
String.Dest: Are you kidding me? I'm one of the best you've got.

String.Source: If we were really "off leash," you'd be one dead breeder by now.
String.Dest: If we were really "off leash," you'd be one dead breeder by now.

String.Source: Why don't you guys come up with some new material?
String.Dest: Why don't you guys come up with some new material?

String.Source: I already did. You're just there as insurance. Now go.
String.Dest: I already did. You're just there as insurance. Now go.

String.Source: Next time you see Nisha, put in a good word for me.
String.Dest: Next time you see Nisha, put in a good word for me.

String.Source: It's only temporary. Lots of changes are happening, and I want our security at its best. Take it as a compliment.
String.Dest: It's only temporary. Lots of changes are happening, and I want our security at its best. Take it as a compliment.

String.Source: Yeah? At least we have the skills to rob a child.
String.Dest: Yeah? At least we have the skills to rob a child.

String.Source: Our own purposes. Salvage what you want, but I want them alive and in one piece.
String.Dest: Our own purposes. Salvage what you want, but I want them alive and in one piece.

String.Source: I know you're the one that locked us in that deathtrap out there. You better watch your back.
String.Dest: I know you're the one that locked us in that deathtrap out there. You better watch your back.

String.Source: Dixie, of course. So you know it's going to be fun.
String.Dest: Dixie, of course. So you know it's going to be fun.

String.Source: You wanted to see me?
String.Dest: Chtěl jsi mě vidět?

String.Source: I finished working on that mod you asked for. It shouldn't affect the balance of the knife once attached.
String.Dest: I finished working on that mod you asked for. It shouldn't affect the balance of the knife once attached.

String.Source: Why don't you guys bathe? Then maybe we would.
String.Dest: Why don't you guys bathe? Then maybe we would.

String.Source: Well, well, look who it is.
String.Dest: Well, well, look who it is.

String.Source: Someone's looking glum. Why the long face?
String.Dest: Someone's looking glum. Why the long face?

String.Source: Shit happens out there in the wasteland. People disappear all the time.
String.Dest: Shit happens out there in the wasteland. People disappear all the time.

String.Source: Nisha? You called?
String.Dest: Nisha? You called?

String.Source: I've heard there's some traders passing through north of the park. I want you to get to them before the others do.
String.Dest: I've heard there's some traders passing through north of the park. I want you to get to them before the others do.

String.Source: I've heard you're responsible for a few of our neighbors' deaths. This needs to stop. You know the plan.
String.Dest: I've heard you're responsible for a few of our neighbors' deaths. This needs to stop. You know the plan.

String.Source: Or maybe you should. Obviously, you suck at it to begin with.
String.Dest: Or maybe you should. Obviously, you suck at it to begin with.

String.Source: Cut myself in three places trying. You gonna show me or do I gotta lose a damn finger first?
String.Dest: Cut myself in three places trying. You gonna show me or do I gotta lose a damn finger first?

String.Source: Sick of this "keeping the peace" bullshit. I got a list of names a mile long that I'm dying to carve up, but Nisha's watching me like a hawk.
String.Dest: Sick of this "keeping the peace" bullshit. I got a list of names a mile long that I'm dying to carve up, but Nisha's watching me like a hawk.

String.Source: What's this? Mason letting you guys roam around off leash?
String.Dest: What's this? Mason letting you guys roam around off leash?

String.Source: Aw, if you can't figure it out soon, come see me. A Disciple that can't do a simple knife trick? I'll put you out of your misery myself.
String.Dest: Aw, if you can't figure it out soon, come see me. A Disciple that can't do a simple knife trick? I'll put you out of your misery myself.

String.Source: Good, this is just what I wanted.
String.Dest: Good, this is just what I wanted.

String.Source: You bet your ass it is. Just don't forget who hooked you up.
String.Dest: You bet your ass it is. Just don't forget who hooked you up.

String.Source: Please, it's not like people I hate just disappear into thin air. I mean, you're still here, aren't you?
String.Dest: Please, it's not like people I hate just disappear into thin air. I mean, you're still here, aren't you?

String.Source: I want you on a run with Dixie. You know how enthusiastic she gets. Make sure she doesn't wipe out the whole settlement.
String.Dest: I want you on a run with Dixie. You know how enthusiastic she gets. Make sure she doesn't wipe out the whole settlement.

String.Source: You want them for our own purposes? Or for the park?
String.Dest: You want them for our own purposes? Or for the park?

String.Source: Savoy said you wanted to see me?
String.Dest: Savoy said you wanted to see me?

String.Source: No way. Too many things I don't trust around here right now.
String.Dest: No way. Too many things I don't trust around here right now.

String.Source: Whatever, Pack-hole. Robbing kids ain't even worth our time.
String.Dest: Kdykoliv, Šelmičko. No, okrádání dětí nestojí za náš čas.

String.Source: I don't want to hear your sob story. Get your shit together, or you can join her.
String.Dest: I don't want to hear your sob story. Get your shit together, or you can join her.

String.Source: Told you that dog won't hunt. But you can still run your pretty, little idea by me tomorrow. You know where to find me.
String.Dest: Told you that dog won't hunt. But you can still run your pretty, little idea by me tomorrow. You know where to find me.

String.Source: Oh god, not you again.
String.Dest: Oh god, not you again.

String.Source: Depends. Who's leading?
String.Dest: Depends. Who's leading?

String.Source: Are you arguing with me? I didn't think so.
String.Dest: Are you arguing with me? I didn't think so.

String.Source: Where's Victor? I know you've done something with him.
String.Dest: Where's Victor? I know you've done something with him.

String.Source: Oh yeah, like she'll listen to me. Talk to her yourself if you want to reign her in.
String.Dest: Oh yeah, like she'll listen to me. Talk to her yourself if you want to reign her in.

String.Source: Yeah, yeah. Savoy said he'd rather skin himself alive than listen to another one of my ideas. He can kiss my ass.
String.Dest: Yeah, yeah. Savoy said he'd rather skin himself alive than listen to another one of my ideas. He can kiss my ass.

String.Source: Pin the tail on the Pack-hole tonight. You in?
String.Dest: Dnes večer zasuneš ocas do Šelmičky. Co ty na to?

String.Source: Savoy said you're getting sloppy. That you've been relying on psycho to complete your...tasks. This needs to stop.
String.Dest: Savoy said you're getting sloppy. That you've been relying on psycho to complete your...tasks. This needs to stop.

String.Source: That's 'cause we want to run this place someday, dummy, so until we do, I suggest you wise up. And only a mile? I'm disappointed.
String.Dest: That's 'cause we want to run this place someday, dummy, so until we do, I suggest you wise up. And only a mile? I'm disappointed.

String.Source: Damn, you're right. Might get more action just sticking around here.
String.Dest: Damn, you're right. Might get more action just sticking around here.

String.Source: Don't try to deny it. I know what you've done.
String.Dest: Don't try to deny it. I know what you've done.

String.Source: I'll believe that when I see it.
String.Dest: I'll believe that when I see it.

String.Source: Don't worry, I wasn't expecting anything else from you.
String.Dest: Don't worry, I wasn't expecting anything else from you.

String.Source: I'll follow your orders as a loyal Minuteman, but our friendship is over. I could never trust you like that again.
String.Dest: I'll follow your orders as a loyal Minuteman, but our friendship is over. I could never trust you like that again.

String.Source: Is there anything I can do to make this right between us?
String.Dest: Is there anything I can do to make this right between us?

String.Source: You can't even believe that. Leading Raiders against the Commonwealth is none of my business? You must think I'm a total pushover.
String.Dest: You can't even believe that. Leading Raiders against the Commonwealth is none of my business? You must think I'm a total pushover.

String.Source: We shouldn't be getting involved with these scum.
String.Dest: We shouldn't be getting involved with these scum.

String.Source: You've crossed a line, General. There are some things I can't forgive.
String.Dest: You've crossed a line, General. There are some things I can't forgive.

String.Source: If you or any Minutemen get in my way, I won't hesitate to put you down.
String.Dest: If you or any Minutemen get in my way, I won't hesitate to put you down.

String.Source: I'll think about it.
String.Dest: Budu o tom přemýšlet.

String.Source: But that's in your hands. You can still turn back and try to actually make the Commonwealth a better place.
String.Dest: But that's in your hands. You can still turn back and try to actually make the Commonwealth a better place.

String.Source: No. Not after this.
String.Dest: No. Not after this.

String.Source: Don't think that the Minutemen will stand by and let you bring even more misery to the Commonwealth.
String.Dest: Don't think that the Minutemen will stand by and let you bring even more misery to the Commonwealth.

String.Source: Despite everything you've done, I never thought you'd stoop to become one of the scum that preys on the Commonwealth.
String.Dest: Despite everything you've done, I never thought you'd stoop to become one of the scum that preys on the Commonwealth.

String.Source: I can't believe I'm responsible for putting you in charge of the Minutemen.
String.Dest: I can't believe I'm responsible for putting you in charge of the Minutemen.

String.Source: This is no place for us, General.
String.Dest: This is no place for us, General.

String.Source: What difference do a few more Raiders make, in the end?
String.Dest: What difference do a few more Raiders make, in the end?

String.Source: Some things are unforgivable.
String.Dest: Some things are unforgivable.

String.Source: What are we doing here?
String.Dest: What are we doing here?

String.Source: Nothing wrong with this place that a company of Minutemen couldn't fix.
String.Dest: Nothing wrong with this place that a company of Minutemen couldn't fix.

String.Dest: You'll "think about it"? That's the kind of meaningless bullshit I've come to expect from you.

String.Source: For the Commonwealth's sake, I hope you change your mind and come back to being the General we hoped for.
String.Dest: For the Commonwealth's sake, I hope you change your mind and come back to being the General we hoped for.

String.Source: You can't even look me in the eye and face up to what you've done, huh? Figures.
String.Dest: You can't even look me in the eye and face up to what you've done, huh? Figures.

String.Source: I've left our settlements alone.
String.Dest: I've left our settlements alone.

String.Source: If that means shooting at you and your new friends, so be it.
String.Dest: If that means shooting at you and your new friends, so be it.

String.Source: That's enough out of you, Garvey.
String.Dest: That's enough out of you, Garvey.

String.Source: My choices are none of your business, Garvey.
String.Dest: My choices are none of your business, Garvey.

String.Source: What are you talking about?
String.Dest: O čem to mluvíš?

String.Source: And that's the damned shame of it all.
String.Dest: And that's the damned shame of it all.

String.Source: I guess we understand each other, then.
String.Dest: I guess we understand each other, then.

String.Source: And then you joined up with the scum that prey on the Commonwealth?
String.Dest: And then you joined up with the scum that prey on the Commonwealth?

String.Source: I thought I knew you. I trusted you.
String.Dest: I thought I knew you. I trusted you.

String.Source: Remember whose side you're on, General.
String.Dest: Remember whose side you're on, General.

String.Source: You made your decision. Now live with it.
String.Dest: You made your decision. Now live with it.

String.Source: I trusted you once. Never again.
String.Dest: I trusted you once. Never again.

String.Source: You really think that matters? We're supposed to be driving the Raiders out of the Commonwealth, not inviting them in!
String.Dest: You really think that matters? We're supposed to be driving the Raiders out of the Commonwealth, not inviting them in!

String.Source: You're out of line, Garvey. I'm still the General of the Minutemen.
String.Dest: You're out of line, Garvey. I'm still the General of the Minutemen.

String.Source: I made a mistake. I'll stop helping the Raiders.
String.Dest: Moje chyba. Už dál nehodlám pomáhat nájezdíkům.

String.Source: Us? Like you and me? We're okay, I suppose. Ain't thought too much about it.
String.Dest: Us? Like you and me? We're okay, I suppose. Ain't thought too much about it.

String.Source: I think it'd be best if we went our separate ways.
String.Dest: Myslím, že bude nejlepší, když půjdeme každý svojí cestou.

String.Source: Oh come on, don't make me say it. You know damn well I don't like talking about feelings and shit. We're... we're great. You know that.
String.Dest: Oh come on, don't make me say it. You know damn well I don't like talking about feelings and shit. We're... we're great. You know that.

String.Source: Are things all right between us?
String.Dest: Je mezi náma všechno v pořádku?

String.Source: If you say so... See you back at home, boss.
String.Dest: If you say so... See you back at home, boss.

String.Source: You're the best damn Overboss anybody could ask for, and I just might follow you off the ends of the earth if you asked. That work for ya?
String.Dest: You're the best damn Overboss anybody could ask for, and I just might follow you off the ends of the earth if you asked. That work for ya?

String.Source: Case you hadn't noticed, I got some serious doubts about whether this is gonna work out.
String.Dest: Case you hadn't noticed, I got some serious doubts about whether this is gonna work out.

String.Source: I'd say we're doing pretty good, boss. Things keep going along like this and I ain't gonna have any complaints.
String.Dest: I'd say we're doing pretty good, boss. Things keep going along like this and I ain't gonna have any complaints.

String.Source: We make one hell of a pair, running together like this. I'm friggin' great, boss.
String.Dest: We make one hell of a pair, running together like this. I'm friggin' great, boss.

String.Source: Yeah, maybe not a bad idea. Shit wasn't going so well anyway. You decide you wanna run things a little different, come find me.
String.Dest: Yeah, maybe not a bad idea. Shit wasn't going so well anyway. You decide you wanna run things a little different, come find me.

String.Source: I wanted to know where things stand between us.
String.Dest: I wanted to know where things stand between us.

String.Source: I just wanted to know how you think we're doing.
String.Dest: I just wanted to know how you think we're doing.

String.Source: Things are all right, I guess. Could use a little more action in my opinion, but you're the boss.
String.Dest: Things are all right, I guess. Could use a little more action in my opinion, but you're the boss.

String.Source: Case you hadn't noticed, I got some serious doubts about whether this is gonna work out.
String.Dest: Case you hadn't noticed, I got some serious doubts about whether this is gonna work out.

String.Source: Been a damn fun ride so far. I'm lookin' forward to seeing what kind of trouble we can get into next.
String.Dest: Been a damn fun ride so far. I'm lookin' forward to seeing what kind of trouble we can get into next.

String.Source: Suppose we're doing all right. I ain't looking to bail out on you or nothin'.
String.Dest: Suppose we're doing all right. I ain't looking to bail out on you or nothin'.

String.Source: Bet there's a whole lot of people right now sorry that we teamed up. Me? I think it's turning out to be a damn good idea.
String.Dest: Bet there's a whole lot of people right now sorry that we teamed up. Me? I think it's turning out to be a damn good idea.

String.Source: It's about time we split.
String.Dest: Je na čase se rozdělit.

String.Source: Who the hell do you think you are? We're supposed to be in this for us, making sure we're taken care of.
String.Dest: Who the hell do you think you are? We're supposed to be in this for us, making sure we're taken care of.

String.Source: Ehh, I can't complain, boss. I mean, I could always complain, but I guess I ain't got any real reason to.
String.Dest: Ehh, I can't complain, boss. I mean, I could always complain, but I guess I ain't got any real reason to.

String.Source: Heh, ain't no place I'd rather be than here with you. That answer your question?
String.Dest: Heh, ain't no place I'd rather be than here with you. That answer your question?

String.Source: It's time we parted company.
String.Dest: Je na čase se rozloučit.

String.Source: I seen some guys go soft, but you... It's embarrassing. Get your shit together.
String.Dest: I seen some guys go soft, but you... It's embarrassing. Get your shit together.

String.Source: Just wanted to check in, make sure we're doing okay.
String.Dest: Jen si chci zkontrolovat, že je mezi námi všechno v pohodě.

String.Source: I ain't had this good a time in... well, maybe ever. You don't have nothing to worry about.
String.Dest: I ain't had this good a time in... well, maybe ever. You don't have nothing to worry about.

String.Source: Is everything okay between us?
String.Dest: Je mezi námi všechno v pořádku?

String.Source: You sure know how to have a good time, I'll give you that.
String.Dest: You sure know how to have a good time, I'll give you that.

String.Source: It's time we part ways.
String.Dest: Nastal čas, kdy se rozdělíme.

String.Source: You should head back.
String.Dest: Měl by ses vydat zpátky.

String.Source: Yeah, suppose I needed a break from actually having a good time anyway. You know where to find me.
String.Dest: Yeah, suppose I needed a break from actually having a good time anyway. You know where to find me.

String.Source: Are you serious with this? After the way you been acting? The hell's the matter with you?
String.Dest: Are you serious with this? After the way you been acting? The hell's the matter with you?

String.Source: Yeah, probably the smartest thing all around. Don't want things getting any worse.
String.Dest: Yeah, probably the smartest thing all around. Don't want things getting any worse.

String.Source: Yeah, all right boss. I'll head on home.
String.Dest: Yeah, all right boss. I'll head on home.

String.Source: You sure? Okay, well don't go gettin' yourself into too much trouble without me.
String.Dest: You sure? Okay, well don't go gettin' yourself into too much trouble without me.

String.Source: What, you getting nervous or somethin'? Don't worry, boss. I only got eyes for you.
String.Dest: What, you getting nervous or somethin'? Don't worry, boss. I only got eyes for you.

String.Dest: We're good. We'd be better if we were getting rich and killing chumps instead of standing around yapping, but that's just me.

String.Source: Hell, right now only thing I'm sorry for is that we didn't meet up sooner.
String.Dest: Hell, right now only thing I'm sorry for is that we didn't meet up sooner.

String.Source: Things are pretty fucking terrible, in case you hadn't noticed. Get your head outta your ass, boss.
String.Dest: Things are pretty fucking terrible, in case you hadn't noticed. Get your head outta your ass, boss.

String.Source: What?
String.Dest: Cože?

String.Source: Everything okay, boss?
String.Dest: Everything okay, boss?

String.Source: You're a real stunner, you know that?
String.Dest: You're a real stunner, you know that?

String.Source: You got something for me, boss?
String.Dest: You got something for me, boss?

String.Source: This better be good.

String.Dest: Hey, you doing all right?

String.Source: You need something, boss?
String.Dest: You need something, boss?

String.Source: What the hell do you want now?
String.Dest: What the hell do you want now?

String.Source: I'm here if you need me.
String.Dest: I'm here if you need me.

String.Source: Anything I can do for you, boss?
String.Dest: Anything I can do for you, boss?

String.Source: How can I help, boss?
String.Dest: How can I help, boss?

String.Dest: Hey, boss. What can I do for you?

String.Source: What's going on, boss?
String.Dest: What's going on, boss?

String.Dest: You need anything, you just say the word.

String.Dest: Hey, boss.

String.Source: What's up, boss?
String.Dest: What's up, boss?

String.Source: Ain't much in the mood for talking.
String.Dest: Ain't much in the mood for talking.

String.Source: You got something to say?
String.Dest: Chceš něco říct?

String.Source: Make it fast.

String.Source: Spit it out.
String.Dest: Spit it out.

String.Source: Ain't you got something better to do?
String.Dest: Ain't you got something better to do?

String.Source: You okay, boss?
String.Dest: You okay, boss?

String.Source: What now?

String.Source: What do you need?

String.Source: Whatever. Told you you'd hate yourself if you didn't come.
String.Dest: Whatever. Told you you'd hate yourself if you didn't come.

String.Source: Shit. I swear to God, that's the last time I'm covering for Kate.
String.Dest: Shit. I swear to God, that's the last time I'm covering for Kate.

String.Source: It was brutal, you would've been all over it. I don't think those farmers suspected a thing. Not like they're alive now to regret it.
String.Dest: It was brutal, you would've been all over it. I don't think those farmers suspected a thing. Not like they're alive now to regret it.

String.Source: Damn it, I knew it. I hate getting stuck with the crap patrol shifts.
String.Dest: Damn it, I knew it. I hate getting stuck with the crap patrol shifts.

String.Source: Last time I had that much fun was when I helped Nisha take out our old gang boss.
String.Dest: Last time I had that much fun was when I helped Nisha take out our old gang boss.

String.Source: How are you always so lucky? Every time I go out, all we find are bullshit bloodworms and ferals.
String.Dest: How are you always so lucky? Every time I go out, all we find are bullshit bloodworms and ferals.

String.Source: How'd it go yesterday?
String.Dest: How'd it go yesterday?

String.Source: What'd I miss?
String.Dest: Co mi uteklo?

String.Source: So, how was it last night?
String.Dest: So, how was it last night?

String.Source: You totally missed out. There was so much blood.
String.Dest: You totally missed out. There was so much blood.

String.Source: Where were you? We took out this whole Super Mutant camp like it was nothing. I haven't had that much fun since we first took this place.
String.Dest: Where were you? We took out this whole Super Mutant camp like it was nothing. I haven't had that much fun since we first took this place.

String.Source: It was just what I needed. Came across a bunch of Gunners and wiped them out.
String.Dest: To bylo přesně to, co bylo potřeba. Narazili jsme na spoustu Ranařů a všechny jsme je zlikvidovali.

String.Source: Are you serious? I knew I'd be missing out if I ran with Liv.
String.Dest: Are you serious? I knew I'd be missing out if I ran with Liv.

String.Source: What? Again? Last time I went out all we found was a pack of ghouls and some damn bloodworms.
String.Dest: Co? Znovu? Naposledy když jsem šla ven, tak jediný, na co jsem narazila, byla smečka ghúlů a nějací zatracení krvočervi.

String.Source: Don't worry. We're running again tomorrow. Same time, same place.
String.Dest: Don't worry. We're running again tomorrow. Same time, same place.

String.Source: Chill out. The next run's just around the corner.
String.Dest: Chill out. The next run's just around the corner.

String.Source: Have any gear I can buy off you?
String.Dest: Have any gear I can buy off you?

String.Source: Sure, boss. Take a look.
String.Dest: Sure, boss. Take a look.

String.Source: Hey, got any gear for sale?
String.Dest: Hey, got any gear for sale?

String.Source: Sorry, boss. All my stuff's back in Nuka-Town.
String.Dest: Sorry, boss. All my stuff's back in Nuka-Town.

String.Source: Yeah, here you go.
String.Dest: Jasně, tady máš.

String.Source: Yeah, boss. Here's everything I got.
String.Dest: Yeah, boss. Here's everything I got.

String.Source: Next time we're back in Nuka-Town you're welcome to take a look.
String.Dest: Next time we're back in Nuka-Town you're welcome to take a look.

String.Source: We'd have to go back to Nuka-Town, boss. All my stuff is stashed there.
String.Dest: We'd have to go back to Nuka-Town, boss. All my stuff is stashed there.
